						               													<description>Exclusive mini expansion for backers of the game during the Kickstarter campaign.&amp;#10;This expansion includes 2 new anomalies for ADELE and 4 new objects (2 copies of each) to make your game a little more different.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The new anomalies: Simply add these new tiles to the ones already in the game; just keep in mind they are not suitable for game modes where ADELE plays as an automaton.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Maintenance Robot and  Surprise Attack&amp;#10;&amp;#10;The new objects:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Computer Virus, Portable Charger, PDA, Portable EMP:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;You may just add the new objects to the common pool of objects but there is a risk that some vital objects will become too scarce, like the batteries or the space suits. So it is recommended removing some existing objects when using the new ones as follows:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Computer Virus - remove 1 battery and 1 Stimulants&amp;#10;PDA - remove 1 flashlight and 1 space suit&amp;#10;Portable charger - remove 1 flashlight and 1 pieces&amp;#10;Portable EMP - remove 1 teddy and 1 first aid kit&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
